<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Substitute Fredrik Jensen scored within seconds of coming on as Finland beat Republic of Ireland 1-0.  </p>

<p>Callum Robinson had an opportunity to score for Ireland but was thwarted by Lukas Hradecky.  </p>

<p>Finland striker Teemu Pukki had a shot saved by Darren Randolph early on.  </p>

<p>More to follow...</p>

